{"word":"νοῦς","slug":"νοῦς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>νοῦς</el>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><el>νοός</el>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ dat.\">dat.</a> <b><el>νοΐ</el>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <b><el>νοῦν, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a></el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> obscure]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘capacity to comprehend or discern’, <b>understanding <a href='B:490 24:45'>Lk 24:45</a>; <a href='B:520 7:23'>Ro 7:23</a>, <a href='B:520 7:25'>25</a>; <a href='B:530 14:14'>1 Cor 14:14f</a>, 19; <a href='B:570 4:7'>Phil 4:7</a>; <a href='B:600 2:2'>2 Th 2:2</a>; <a href='B:610 6:5'>1 Ti 6:5</a>; <a href='B:620 3:8'>2 Ti 3:8</a>; <a href='B:630 1:15'>Tit 1:15</a>; <a href='B:730 13:18'>Rv 13:18</a>; <a href='B:730 17:9'>17:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘medium for processing information or instruction’, <b>mind <a href='B:520 1:28'>Ro 1:28</a>; <a href='B:520 12:2'>12:2</a>; <a href='B:530 1:10'>1 Cor 1:10</a>; <a href='B:560 4:17'>Eph 4:17</a>, <a href='B:560 4:23'>23</a>; <a href='B:580 2:18'>Col 2:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘result of mental processing’,<b>mind, thought <a href='B:520 11:34'>Ro 11:34</a>; <a href='B:520 14:5'>14:5</a>; <a href='B:530 2:16'>1 Cor 2:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:νουνεχῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Νύμφα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}